{"tid":1513021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【母親悲慟】廈門18個月B女遭全身鏡砸死 新加坡樟宜機場潮牌店涉事","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:09:03.000Z","uid":53026,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe29f2d827a32a1282d5afcde87fcb49a0f7f93","tid":1513021,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"【母親悲慟】廈門18個月B女遭全身鏡砸死 新加坡樟宜機場潮牌店涉事<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0828 12:24 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0828 06:00<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190827/large/1566921530_f832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190827%2Flarge%2F1566921530_f832.jpg&h=2773a05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（新增內容）有中國版Zara之稱的連鎖服裝店「Urban Revivo」的新加坡樟宜機場分店發生奪命意外，一名18個月大的中國女童，遭店內一塊全身鏡壓倒，當場昏迷，送院後不治。<br />\n<br />\n事發在本月23日下午12時左右，與樟宜機場連接的星耀樟宜商場2樓的「Urban Revivo」門店。據指，意外發生前，有小童在店內嬉戲，擺在一旁的全身鏡，疑因被撞擊倒下，18個月大的女童恰巧就站在全身鏡前，遭倒下的鏡子砸中；鏡子砸中女童後沒有碎裂，但女童鼻嘴流血，當場陷入昏迷。女童因為傷勢過重，返魂乏術。事發後，涉事店面暫停營業，大門外拉起封鎖線，並附上告示指「服裝店因點貨而不營業」。<br />\n<br />\n2006年，Urban Revivo於中國創立，其官方網站顯示，在歐洲、北美、日本等地有200多間分店，其中3間設在新加坡，除了星耀樟宜，獅城大廈和來福士城購物中心也有Urban Revivo分店。<br />\n<br />\n女童家人於24日早上在星耀樟宜職員陪同下，到殮房領屍。身穿白衣白褲的母親由另外4名家人陪同，神情悲痛，數度落淚。店方亦發聲明指，對事件感到難過，正協助緊警方調查，並會支援死者家屬。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡《聯合晚報》"},{"pid":"3709ec6b280fa01c63421d0fa06f732ddac09882","tid":1513021,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"新加坡咁堅都出事？"},{"pid":"2901c27e014eb899f03b1acad9916f28db546ae4","tid":1513021,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5LHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=2a938426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5LHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=4393d18a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5LHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=b4933c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"277952412d99ba750c967a89737e95f077c69b1a","tid":1513021,"uid":301915,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜不論老弱婦孺無一個係無辜㗎"},{"pid":"c3ca152eb5a74244612702debfa04618e716cb0f","tid":1513021,"uid":438,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"自己唔睇實由得佢周圍撞<br />\n自作孽邊怪得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c29b273dc39f81d38848d45a08f060705ac28e","tid":1513021,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCrFNAj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCrFNAj.jpg&h=0b132a02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAK8b10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAK8b10.jpg&h=054ab481&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nRZiG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nRZiG0.jpg&h=372ddf78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTuj28F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTuj