,{"pid":"fa61b7f9e6d3d7932a3d42eae33e11e35a3a80d6","tid":1513021,"uid":218179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"塊鏡冇碎可唔可以留返係到繼續用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f796271507616d179df9809eab84ed92b3cfbf43","tid":1513021,"uid":106634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"啲老母硬係由啲小柒頭四圍跑都唔理，到出咗事又四圍搵人嚟怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3797ef4ffcaa8c66c7ebde88c543b79aa37e632","tid":1513021,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"抵死。<br />\n仲記得係餐廳做，有個支那人的仔女又係周圍撞，同佢的父母講返，佢父母真係唔理。好似佢有食野就係皇帝咁，餐廳拎住熱野避得好辛苦，佢父母真係痴撚線。<br />\n<br />\n香港人的父母起碼都會叫停佢地的子女。"},{"pid":"277ee9621cd9958856617d2b7cff0cce90fd5b3e","tid":1513021,"uid":105059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"周圍撞果個係第二個細路呀"}]}